{
  "stem": "13981.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forget the name of the place where this happened in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the SS had gone underground behind our lines, the local SS people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a German communist, a prisoner of war-- not a-- a civilian had come up and told us that-- what he had picked up information.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we dropped everything else, and were able to get the three head guys, the leaders.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First two, and then the third one, I went to his house several times, and he was never there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But his house was well stocked, as I remember, with black market supplies that nobody else in Germany [LAUGHS] had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, in the meantime, the other two guys had given us information that they had a cage of arms hidden in the ground not too far from the-- where we-- where this other guy lived.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we put a few prisoners of war to work starting to dig out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I went back again, and this time I did find the guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I took my-- it wasn't my .45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was somebody else's .45.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I pointed it at him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, you go 10 feet ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not going to give you any instructions where to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know exactly where I want to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he just took-- made a beeline to the cache of arms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we found bazookas, rifles, bullets, dynamite caps, and the Nazi flag that I have there, that I kept because I figured it-- that is mine.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I told him, now we have all these things here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see what we got here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now tell me, please, where's the dynamite?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The dynamite caps by themselves are practically harmless.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
